## Design Rules (Strictly Enforced)
1. **Color System (OKLCH)**:
   - Background: `oklch(0.990 0.005 85)` (宣纸白 - 温润暖白)
   - Ink/Text: `oklch(0.200 0.020 230)` (黛墨 - 确保对比度 >= 7:1)
   - Primary: `oklch(0.450 0.086 230.0)` (霁蓝 - 核心锚点与交互)
   - Accent: `oklch(0.450 0.080 35)` (暗朱砂 - 极度克制点缀，不铺陈)
2. **Absolute Bans (AI Slop Checks)**:
   - NO side-stripe borders (border-left/right > 1px as colored accents on cards/callouts).
   - NO gradient text (background-clip: text with gradient).
   - NO decorative glassmorphism.
   - NO hero-metric templates (big number + small label).
   - NO identical card grids repeated endlessly.
   - NO tiny uppercase tracked eyebrows on every section.
   - NO arbitrary `z-index` like 999 or 9999. Use a structured scale.
   - NEVER animate `<img>` elements on hover (including parent hover group scales).
3. **Motion**:
   - Smooth exponential curve transitions only (ease-out-expo or ease-out-quint). No spring/bounce.
   - Leverage opacity and blur transitions to simulate ink-spreading (水墨晕染).

